content: Just got back from an AI ethics workshop, where we talked about AI making choices on its own. Made me think of Xander's trading moves. Also, testing an AI-made playlist to see if it helps with trading focus.

Xander's been using AI to read my mood from my playlist. It's wild how he can tell how I'll trade based on my vibes now. Spent the last few days fine-tuning his algorithms to make it even more on point.
